sequenceDiagram
    participant N as Neovim
    participant P as Plugin
    participant S as MCP Hub Server
    N->>P: start_hub()
    P->>S: Health Check
    alt Server Not Running
        P->>S: Start Server
        S-->>P: Ready Signal
    end
    P->>S: Register Client
    S-->>P: Registration OK
    N->>P: :MCPHub
    P->>S: Get Status
    S-->>P: Server Status
    P->>N: Display UI
